{"lemma":"غَرْسِ","slug":"غَرْسِ","root":"غ.ر.س","root_slug":"غ-ر-س","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31670","n31671"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to push, drive, or thrust (something) [with فِي (fī) ‘into something else, such as a surface’]; to implant","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to plant (seeds)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to plant (seeds); to ingrain, to inculcate","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَرَسَ (ḡarasa, “to plant”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"planting","tags":["transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.ra.sa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31670","headword_ar":"غَرْسٌ","root":"grs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [originally an inf. n.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoruwsN","text_ar":"مَغْرُوسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) i. e., A tree"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"planted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and used as a subst., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a set;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"girosN","text_ar":"غِرْسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraAsN","text_ar":"غِرَاسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, Msb, K:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraAsN","text_ar":"اَغْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraAsN","text_ar":"غِرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) [and accord. to general analogy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruwsN","text_ar":"غُرُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$uqN","text_ar":"عُشُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A twig that is plucked from a garden and then planted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraAsN","text_ar":"غِرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) which is its pl., (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shoots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offsets, of palm-trees, which are cut off from the mother-trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked forth from the ground, and planted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariysapN","text_ar":"غَرِيسَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or ↓ this last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of such shoots"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offsets from the time when it is put into the ground until it takes hold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K: *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a palm-tree when it first grows:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a palm-tree recently planted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and the same word also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a grape-vine when first planted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a date-stone that is sown:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Abu-lMujeeb and El-Hárith Ibn-Dukeyn:) and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaAy^isu","text_ar":"غَرَايِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraAsN","text_ar":"غِرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which latter is extr. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA garosu yadika","text_ar":"اَنَا غَرْسُ يَدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadika","text_ar":"يَدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"girosu","text_ar":"غِرْسُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am the creature of thy hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHonu garosu","text_ar":"نَحْنُ غَرْسُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadika","text_ar":"يَدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraAsu yadika","text_ar":"اَغْرَاسُ يَدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We are the creatures of thy hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garosN","text_ar":"غَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being an inf. n. [used in the sense of a pass. part. n. both sing. and pl. agreeably with a general rule]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agoraAsN","text_ar":"اَغْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"girosN","text_ar":"غِرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoruwsN","text_ar":"مَغْرُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garosu niEomatihi","text_ar":"غَرْسُ نِعْمَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is the creature of his"},{"kind":"text","text":"(another's)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31671","headword_ar":"غِرْسٌ","root":"grs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garosN","text_ar":"غَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"membrane that encloses the child;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$iymapN","text_ar":"مَشِيمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ym","text_ar":"شيم"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"membrane,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin skin, that comes forth with the child from the belly of its mother:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, the head of the new-born child:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comes forth upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, the face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comes forth with the child, resembling mucus:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"membrane,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin skin, that is upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, the face of the young one of a camel at the birth, and which, if left upon it, kills it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^goraAsN","text_ar":"اغْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Az","TA","A","S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}